{"tid":2056394,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 我想寫一首關於香港既長篇敘事詩","createTime":"2020-06-08T15:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T00:07:35.000Z","uid":40368,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"142389a64401679c5766ecdfbb38ec43465fed5c","tid":2056394,"uid":40368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"我想寫一首關於香港既長篇敘事詩<br />\n靈感源自睇白居易《長恨歌》，覺得可以用長篇敘事詩既形式<br />\n記述香港過去呢段日子發生既事，同埋抒發對社會變遷既感受<br />\n我想收集大家呢一年既感受，同埋大家認為一定要寫落詩中既大事件<br />\n<br />\n暫時我構思將詩分為四部份，第一部份寫香港回歸至今概況、第二部份寫反送中始末、第三部份寫武肺政策、第四部份寫國安法<br />\n<br />\n暫時起左幾句頭，成首詩大約會係咁樣形式寫落去：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>百年逆旅經飛雨，南港起風如細語。<br />\n逍遙歸客厭樊籠，回首滄桑常側佇。<br />\n<br />\n可憐柳絮隨風舞，任憑業火化焦土。<br />\n英倫不識稷狐奸，百千里地呈胡虜。<br />\n<br />\n合浦珠還作芥塵，一朝天子一朝臣。<br />\n秦王不識邯鄲璧，只得離形不得神。<br />\n<br />\n往來災殃強自尊，多少戾沓任嘲喧。<br />\n浮華漸逝無人惜，遍地吏饕盡詐諼。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我係照住《長恨歌》既平仄格律去寫，想模仿一下呢首我好鍾意既長詩<br />\n自問唔係白居易，寫唔到佢咁層次豐腴、淒美動人<br />\n當中不少大家可以指教之處，亦盼大家不吝賜教<br />\n希望可以用詩句去記錄，跪求大家俾啲靈感我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739bd146aa0fec81e11daab493500ac36506c6ec","tid":2056394,"uid":40368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"無論係你呢段日子既感受，或者你覺得一定要記載既事<br />\n都可以架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0a1e99cc6c9199163a23b3c630110a333f0c05","tid":2056394,"uid":143257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"巴打有料<br />\n文學嘢唔叻<br />\n不過都feel到好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得可以提埋14年雨傘 做個過渡？<br />\n鳩up"},{"pid":"c684a29bd75523f3a326ab621b8cd3cd3451bdf5","tid":2056394,"uid":40368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a0a1e99cc6c9199163a23b3c630110a333f0c05","tid":2056394,"uid":143257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"巴打有料<br />\n文學嘢唔叻<br />\n不過都feel到好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得可以提埋14年雨傘 做個過渡？<br />\n鳩up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點同你比<br />\n我會寫雨革，印象深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a08c2b80e030cd9546c363d3e07b3403e468bdd","tid":2056394,"uid":40368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcce6eee4ad186c29f38ec3ef729998c0b2d85e","tid":2056394,"uid":11237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"幫手一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1adb9f906f0c23e3bb1fe48eac0167e80b0895","tid":2056394,"uid":235585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點將黑警死全家寫成詩"},{"pid":"ccfd14fbbfd9480be1d8392f90aebe6d29c32c60","tid":2056394,"uid":287096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T00:07:35.000Z","msg":"用最後一段寫鼓勵香港人要有希望？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}